<div style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 120px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Function_ocsillating_at_3_hertz.svg" class="image" title="Function ocsillating at 3 hertz.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c3/Function_ocsillating_at_3_hertz.svg/120px-Function_ocsillating_at_3_hertz.svg.png" width="120" height="103" border="0" /></a></div>
</div>
<div class="gallerytext">
<p>Original function showing oscillation 3 hertz.</p>
</div>
</div>
</td>
<td>
