<p><img class="tex" alt="\int_{\mathbb{R}^n}f(x) e^{-i x\cdot\nu }\, dx " src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/math/4/3/d/43d577f648e04cfb28a80a380606e1aa.png" /></p>
